  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to compare the antibody response 30 days after two doses of t
      OPV
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The trial design is phase II, randomized, double blind, prospective intervention study. The
      subject study are 240 healthy, full term, newborn infants.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
